###### Question


Find the area in the first quadrant between the lines $y=x$, $y=1$, and the curve $y=x^2 + 4$.

::: {.cell hold='true' execution_count=37}

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display execution_count=38}
```{=html}
<form class="mx-2 my-3 mw-100" name='WeaveQuestion' data-id='13072349269886558537' data-controltype=''>
  <div class='form-group '>
    <div class='controls'>
